Jim Furyk beat Kevin Kisner in a playoff at the 17th hole to win the RBC Heritage at Hilton Head . 
  The 2010 US Open champion hit a final round 63 to finish 18-under in regulation play . 
  Furyk won his first PGA Tour title since 2010 at Harbour Town . 
  Troy Merritt finished second and Jordan Spieth tied 11th . 
 